## Setup Instructions

### 1. Clone the Repository
```bash
git clone https://github.com/Divian29/Box-item-management.git
cd Box-item-management

############ Build the Project #######
mvn clean install

####### Run the Project#####
mvn spring-boot:run

#####Testing with Postman####

Open Postman

Create a new collection Box & Item Management

Test the endpoints:

POST /boxes

GET /boxes

GET /boxes/{id}

POST /items

GET /items

**GET /items/{id}`


